Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:05.54,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)\an3\fs22\pos(585,288)}第7話  「圖書部的休息日」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:31.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(540,0)}下集  「魔法之書」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:48.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:54.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:46.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:48.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:54.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:46.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看筧那個樣子實際上也有迷糊的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該喜歡細心會照顧人的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會喜歡會做飯的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前他說過會做馬鈴薯燉肉的女生很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長是很酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該喜歡同類型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  他很會配合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能喜歡會賣傻的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能得出結論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  筧的女友不是小太刀妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的確常和小太刀學姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看上去不像是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能問筧學長了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀  這次的委託是不能告訴筧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個  你這星期天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  如果不介意的話  請和我們約會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.03,TXTI,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(133,263)}星  期  日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太吵了  小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  現在幾點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讀書讀到早晨  然後睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會遲到  是不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是筧同學的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用下冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  出門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長不遲到的話  現在早在外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有沒洗的餐具  放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就好  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黑死館殺人事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「腦髓地獄」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「獻給虛無的供物」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是傳說中的三大奇書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：這三本書並稱日本三大推理奇書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  書要放在書架上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看著不舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該放整齊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂吧  又不是你住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  當然不會住  我在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說怎麼一大早就吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都來家裡表現自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼隨便就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計較什麼  常有的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是鄰居啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是可以隨便出入的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是要去買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  你有什麼喜歡的店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有常去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道好店的話就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常去的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多可愛風格的  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我穿了這種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會有人報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我覺得你很適合呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  至少不會有人報警的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就開始櫻庭學姐改變形象大作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件很合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  可愛得不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件也適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳踏四條船的約會  真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是她們買東西的跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看上去很開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的真命天女是哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能隨便選  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要腳踏四條船弄成修羅場喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望鄰居家出命案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  該說「你真可愛  甜心」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11點45分開始吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排得真細
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想好了時間表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  完美的約會路線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因  因為白崎很期待約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你調查得好詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  最後去的能看到夕陽的小丘公園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向意中人告白的經典場所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒時間了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長的隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為美食節目介紹過好幾次這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  排隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  現在排估計要等上一小時的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我應該預約的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  這樣正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月我手頭緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難得你找了家好店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去那種店我更安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不會變通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種固執不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧和小玉果然般配
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不刻意地為女性圓場  得分很高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起戀人  更像是搭擋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人想比試比試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園你玩這種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我每天都有鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道看哪裡好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  方便活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我  有多餘的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下好  得分很高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣看起來好像被命令舔腳的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開玩笑  看來沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拍過那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就都是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百萬伏特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  再靠近些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不好意思了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  朋友說  有的情侶會在這密閉空間接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉那種讓人放不下的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能正合筧學長性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看上去是御園在以欺負筧為樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢  我找了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工廠攝影集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助你興趣好特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  同好其實有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  這些都要買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月不是手頭緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以挑了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些書真是種類各異啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長難道你是濫讀型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是不挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什麼推薦的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡什麼樣的書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這樣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次和男生談書談得這麼投機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣相投果然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長和佳奈在一起時總是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是好搭擋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.33,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2DDD2&\frx6\fry342\pos(329,256)\frz13.9}懸疑類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的在圖書部下賭注的事  怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然記得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得是重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  是賭贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  習慣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被有特別感情的人看著的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.50,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HFFFDFF&}你了解真正的自己嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我記得這裡有飲食區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  愉快的約會到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來有牧羊人的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎的命運將要發生巨大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎她？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來很有可能以藝術家的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下許多名垂青史的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是即將發生的與白崎的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會極大地改變他的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對白崎一見鐘情  當場向她表白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被委婉拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不肯放棄  不停繼續著攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…變成跟蹤狂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  貌似放棄了對白崎的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他發揮了他所有的藝術細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出了絕讚的充氣娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為：白崎妹妹18號！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎妹妹18號在全世界激起了巨大的熱潮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而白崎作為白崎妹妹18號的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名垂青史
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不是什麼不好的未來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那娃娃看起來那麼棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  充氣娃娃是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是什麼…難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用來幹那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟有多變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}那個  我想單吃甜點的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  這樣下去會相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學　在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也很可愛呢　我的甜心  緒美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  筧同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒美  我可以抱得更緊一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧…同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男的和白崎的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該朝著好的方向發展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  你這是何等的粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面是有原因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  聽我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小太刀的合謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為你們好像背著筧在做著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們也主動出擊試探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒頭沒腦地說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  我們哪會在背地裡搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  怎麼會在背地裡對筧同學做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎學姐  你太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總算清楚  你是一個不會撒謊的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  向筧坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道我喜歡的類型？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:23.10,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(262,55,-80,55,21,6486)}標題：關於圖書部的筧同學    發信人：希望匿名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:23.10,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(278,196,-64,196,21,6486)}我喜歡筧同學。能告訴我筧同學喜歡的類型嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們不清楚筧同學喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想以我們4人為例的話  會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名啊  肯定是惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  多人約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名沒被邀請的可憐部員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  cry  boy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀左大人！只有你能理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遭到反感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人情報的收集區塊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西是什麼時候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢  很久之前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會做這種東西  想不起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰有什麼頭緒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學呢  你有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前牧羊人不是給我們過發郵件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們就想弄清牧羊人的真實身份…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是老了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我筧同學喜歡的類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是希望你能幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我想幫你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連咨詢郵件都發了  而你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也成為牧羊人的話  會被大家遺忘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那麼晚才注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魔法圖書館時我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都擁有記載自己人生的書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  牧羊人沒有屬於自己的書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確地說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「書」這一人類的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成為牧羊人的時候將被抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以牧羊人不會給人留下記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再有壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超越人類的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心不下同伴們  跟她們愉快地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗地裡卻以牧羊人的身份奉獻他人奉獻社會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道還以為能這麼美好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不付出任何代價就想得到巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上哪有那麼簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就算如此你也想當牧羊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜放棄與白崎她們的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個遊樂場非常有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個星期日如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時間喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去乘坐各種嚇人設施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從什麼時候開始  變得不想捨棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要放棄牧羊人考試的話請趁早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甘願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為牧羊人  從所有人的記憶中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為牧羊人  引導世界向著好的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  我已經做好放棄一切的覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我也會忘了你的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你會忘記我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣  你也同樣會把我忘得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經捨棄一切了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要強烈質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我在圖書部毫無地位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為圖書部創始人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近完全淪為龍套了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連休息日都沒被邀請參加多人約會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有存在意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  能幫我拿一下架子上的盒子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常樂意
